Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼們 都碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個光輝是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口在癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 那傢伙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總算趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法在寺院裡張開防禦牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這道結界只要不從我的意識內消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:38.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就會消除陣內所有傷害我們的靈體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:44.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會認同的那樣的邪術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:52.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這四色之光是幽界深處保護我們疼愛我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,偉大存在之靈力於現世展露之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:03.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那偉大的存在 就是你們法王廳的聖典內記載的四方的守護天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管表述的語言多麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:09.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽就是太陽 光芒就是光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使念誦的經文不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:13.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尋求救贖的心卻相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把差異當成區分和虐待人的原因 是愚蠢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神的名義是屬於神的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人所統轄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:29.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為何我們的經文中沒有這些力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能像你的咒文那樣召喚奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:38.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寺院是為了使人和天使精靈會面的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術師會自己在心中築造神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要相信眼睛看不到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有懷疑的餘地的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就去看 去感覺 去觸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:59.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不得了的小姑娘啊
Comment: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.66,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨龜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那種怪物會出現在現世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,區區巨鬼是無法進入這個結界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個結界對幽體有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對物體無效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出現了這種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不創造機會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,創造施展法術的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 司令員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等 那傢伙在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼樣也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會被踩扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙很適應這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和我說的一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經覺得他超乎常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到已經到如此地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣就幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用魔法只憑自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一個人類能達到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大傢伙獨有的頑強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和雜兵不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在手臂接好之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是川馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:28.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,川馬就是讓旅行者在河中溺水的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只巨鬼連川馬也出現了為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是雨 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是個怪物卻會用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,川馬是中位靈格的水妖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,同族的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易驅使沒有自我的低級元素們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天的川馬是非常危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有視覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是順著自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉罕見的活人的幽體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:06.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅有獸鬼 連巨鬼和川馬也出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拿獸鬼做對手還可以 但
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是和敵人周旋 爭取些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女小姐就趁機念咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好保護卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:30.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼短時間內能把風元素活用到如此程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:46.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法解放你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在你旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我沒想過這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我的半身一樣的另一個被鎖著的靈魂在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我被黑暗包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這也要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:13.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼至少我要在暴風雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓半身被撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:20.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,風之精靈啊 給予我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別摔跤比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個馬蟾蜍很適合做我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也容易理解這邊的傢伙 對我的路子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,單槍匹馬就把那個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快當廢物使了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候我什麼也辦不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:23.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,德·卡普拉... ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趕緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:28.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,往深處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比這層幽界更深一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個寺院建成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,位於這個山丘的神殿的幽體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水之元素
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻擊都被水牆阻擋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,與此相比 我卻不能防住所有的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到水花會有這樣的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作為魔法初學者 已是無計可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:27.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高的樣子不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止會發射水花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就在地上淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多虧這些我也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,風的力量不止是把東西斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 精靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能斬開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,捲起來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:31.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 塞爾彼高那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:54.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 會掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水從川馬身上離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:09.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼 看見了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是水的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基現在和水的精靈成為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被附體啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水的眷屬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,流經此地的谷河的精靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遵從古老的誓約
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,清洗汙染這片土地的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我以水底的貴婦人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向元素靈們發令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把這土地上的邪惡靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用激流沖回冥界的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是水本身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 我的眷屬們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 聚集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,翻滾 流動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這回又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河水泛濫 朝這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快進來 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會被捲進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:23.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼 怪物們都被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 我們得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人 魔女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,辦到了 多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子全部幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多再不醒過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:57.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 和水精同步太強失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法術解不開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 史爾基小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在施術的時候被強行喚回會發生什麼事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在史爾基已經去了幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:18.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才的水精融為一體 現在一定被困在這流水中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在心回來之前就喚醒 不知道會對身體産生什麼影響
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有不慎 也許會不能回復自我變成廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底要怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那個 我記得這個時候要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個杖打拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:39.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以一定的節奏打拍子 令施術者的精神集中在現世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,科羅拉這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,節奏是七·七·七拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,打三次七拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,流動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,捲起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用人語表達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令人焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和精靈們心靈交融非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可被其吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:06.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此魔法師會在施術是用杖打拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來確保自己的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:14.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔道 絶不是與力量融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼 打起精神來 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:24.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到那兩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:38.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急 現在史爾基在尋找兩人的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我沉溺於力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是再做好一些的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這麼緊張的話 平時做得到的事也會失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:58.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你拯救了這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人會責備你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:21.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 到底要怎樣才能做到那麼厲害的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:43.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,借助天使和精靈的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救這個村子的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:50.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家教典裡的守護東西南北的四大天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有在建起寺院之前 這片土地祭祀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河底的貴婦人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:03.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我曾經聽爺爺說過這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:09.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這片山丘以前建有祭祀河神的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為長期被遺忘 這次又突然叫出來的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精靈有些生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此村子才會被水淹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不成熟的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,房子再建就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:30.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能這樣活著 都是靠你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:32.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我心中對村民的憤怒導致的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人 可以的話在這個廣場的西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能建個祭祀河神的小祠堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:47.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就建吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寬容也是神的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:56.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣的小孩子也能引起那樣的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰都可以用魔法的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:02.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用魔法要花很長時間修行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:07.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把願望傳達給天使和精靈你們也能辦的到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個方法祭司很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:19.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別理我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子你才是沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到處亂走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,託那個小個子的福已經好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先跟你道個謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受不起你這個拯救村子的英雄的謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甭抬舉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:38.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個四處大吵大鬧的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我有想要給你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:53.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我父親從海員那裡賭贏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這種小尺寸小孩子也揮的起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個老人的餞別禮罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從家計和病重的母親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從所有沉重繁瑣的東西中逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想也真是奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:20.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得是勇敢的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但也覺得是天真的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才說你們上年紀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了老頭 我那個叫野心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和天真的夢想等級可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要證明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本事是貨真價實的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:45.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 東西我就心懷感激的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:51.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就行動是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個寺院的魔法效果還沒完全消散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住上一晚傷口就該好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:00.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有等待的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早一刻也好 趕緊出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要發呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:21.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.64,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.26,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝我們吧
Comment: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.55,EDCht,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.23,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}緋紅序幕  緩緩拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:53.18,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}笑談之間  揭開舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.11,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}台上一切  皆為戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:00.53,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}循序漸進  如詩如畫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:10.12,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}一字之差  終局俱變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:18.60,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}索然無味  其為傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.92,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}利慾之心  隱於夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.99,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}日升之前  一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.66,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}純真羽翼  散落人間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.36,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}應著之色  是黑是白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:39.44,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}不得而知  好奇尚異
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:43.32,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}餘音裊裊  不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.24,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}何人願聞  何人可應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:52.39,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}虛浮年華  何需再度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.23,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}鮮明な赤の緞帳を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:53.18,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}歓声の中  舞台へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.11,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}全て予定調和の戯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:00.53,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}狂いは無い  絵画の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:10.12,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}たった一字が欠けた時に結末は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:18.60,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}呆気無い程に  それが 物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.92,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}夜に隠したambition  greed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.99,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}朝が来る前に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.66,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}無邪気に散り降る羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.36,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}染まるべき色は白か黒か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:39.44,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}知らない  知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:43.32,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}木霊するostinato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.24,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}誰か聴いて  誰か応えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:52.39,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}仮初の日々はもう要らない
Comment: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.35,OPCht,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:25.17,OPCht,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:34.63,OPCht,,0,0,0,,任憑他人道長短  殊死之斗又何曾徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:44.97,OPCht,,0,0,0,,暗啞了的嘶吼  依舊在耳畔激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:51.22,OPCht,,0,0,0,,笑至盡頭之人不是我  亦無怨無悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.13,OPCht,,0,0,0,,唯願能夠守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:00.77,OPCht,,0,0,0,,誅盡來敵戰至終
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.46,OPCht,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:08.40,OPCht,,0,0,0,,思思纏繞神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.92,OPCht,,0,0,0,,欲斷枷鎖魂難斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.70,OPCht,,0,0,0,,若能終結一切以戰止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.21,OPCht,,0,0,0,,焚盡我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:30.58,OPCht,,0,0,0,,困獸猶鬥  逆境之中尋生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:25.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:34.63,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:44.97,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:51.22,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.13,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:00.77,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.46,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:08.40,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.92,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.70,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.21,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:30.58,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.54,Preview,,0,0,0,,腐朽之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:11.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}是幽界的黑暗領域 克里科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你來殿後 保護女人們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你的靈魂和這樣的\N克里科特很相配
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你在窺視深淵的時候 \N深淵也在窺視你
